Using #torgersontailcare is what got her tail so long and healthy! 🤩 

I often get asked "what products do you use?"

@manentailequine shampoo and conditioner is what I use for her body and legs. You can actually get this at your local grocery store, feed store, and off of Amazon! 

Next, I use @exhibitorsequine purple shampoo for her mane, tail, and socks! This stuff is magic! I just order it off Amazon! 

After she's done drying, I spray her down with some @farnamhorse laser sheen! I swear by this stuff! It smells amazing and the shine is real! 😍 You can get this in a concentrate and just dilute it with water. I get mine from my local feed store, or off Amazon! 

QOTD: How often do you wash your horse(s)?
AOTD: I wash Frenchy once or twice a month! And kiss, probably once a month! 

